  "title": "LoadReturn",
  "description": "Maps a Loadable constructor to the concrete type returned by Loader.load. Token classes (Json, TextAsset, SvgAsset, VttAsset) are special-cased because their return types do not match their constructor type. All other loadables return the instance type inferred from the constructor.",
